platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Fans of critically acclaimed CBS series like The Good Fight, NCIS, The Stand, and The Late Show With Stephen Colbert will love Paramount+. Sports fans can stream the NCAA tournament, the UEFA Champions League, the NFL on CBS, and the Masters. Newshounds can tune in to 60 Minutes and CBS Evening News. Star Trek series past, present, and future are establishing their home base here too. And there’s loads to watch with kids, including Dora the Explorer, Paw Patrol, Blue’s Clues, and the best of Nickelodeon’s streaming catalog.
